sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant A as App Adapter
  participant Core as @llm-translator/core
  participant Store as StorageAdapter
  participant LLM as OpenAI-Compatible LLM

  U->>A: 选中文本并触发翻译
  A->>Store: getSettings + getGlossary
  A->>Core: translate(request, storage)
  Core->>Store: getCache(cacheKey)
  alt 命中缓存
    Core-->>A: translatedText (fromCache=true)
  else 未命中缓存
    Core->>LLM: chat/completions
    LLM-->>Core: translatedText
    Core->>Store: setCache
    Core-->>A: translatedText (fromCache=false)
  end
  A-->>U: 临时展示结果 / 可 Pin
